<plot>In the dark corridors of a huge monastery, a verger makes his rounds and comes upon a little girl, apparently left behind. Sadistically, he tells her of the dead priest haunting the place, enjoying her look of fear. Moments later, he himself becomes the victim of the clerical apparition's merciless wrath, for he has woefully miscalculated the nature of the little girl.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?363359</url></doc>
